## YOUTUBE THUMBNAIL IMAGE GENERATION PROMPT

**Visual Concept:**

Create a striking 16:9 YouTube thumbnail showing a visual split-screen philosophical opposition. 

LEFT SIDE (Hindu Moksha):
- Bright golden-white radiant light emanating from center
- Image of a meditating figure surrounded by lotus flowers and temple architecture
- Upward-pointing light rays suggesting ascension and continuation
- Warm golden and white color palette
- Symbolic imagery: eternal flame, infinite light, divine radiance
- Text overlay: "MOKSHA" in large gold Sanskrit-styled font

RIGHT SIDE (Buddhist Nirvana):
- Deep indigo/dark blue or cool neutral tone
- Image of peaceful emptiness, void, or serene meditation figure surrounded by minimal space
- Downward or inward-pointing energy suggesting dissolution
- Cool tones: silver, deep blue, twilight purple
- Symbolic imagery: extinguishing flame, infinite void, peaceful darkness
- Text overlay: "NIRVANA" in silver/white clean modern font

CENTER DIVIDING LINE:
- Bold separator showing the philosophical opposition
- Add a question mark or VS symbol at the center to highlight the contradiction

TOP BANNER:
- Add bold text: "MOKSHA vs NIRVANA?" or "THEY'RE OPPOSITES"
- High contrast, readable at thumbnail size

BOTTOM TEXT SUGGESTION:
- "The Truth Nobody Talks About"
- OR "Why They're Not the Same"
- In contrasting color to background

OVERALL STYLE: Professional, scholarly, mysterious. High contrast for visibility at small sizes. Cinematic lighting. The two halves should look complementary but distinctly opposed‚Äînot harmonious.

